This lesson is based on two sets of materials. The first is my tutorial on counting distribution. You down load it from my web site at ^*Hwww.hondobridge.com^*N. That is where most of the material will come from. Also, for those of you who have Marty Bergen's ^*IDeclarer Play^*N book, there is some material from Chapter two. I will note where the material comes from for each hand. |
